sql_prompt: Find all work orders that are currently 'In Progress'.
sql: SELECT * FROM wo.DUPLO_WORK_ORDER WHERE WORK_ORDER_STATUS = 'In Progress'
sql_context:
CREATE TABLE wo.DUPLO_WORK_ORDER (
                WORK_ORDER_ID VARCHAR(50), -- A unique identifier for each work order. Use this for specific lookups.
                ASSET_ID VARCHAR(50), -- The ID of the physical asset (e.g., equipment, machinery) that the work order is for.
                WORKFLOW_CODE VARCHAR(100), -- A code representing the process or sequence of steps for the work order.
                WORK_ORDER_STATUS VARCHAR(100), -- The current state of the work order (e.g., 'In Progress', 'Completed', 'Canceled').
                DUE_DATE DATE, -- The date by which the work order must be completed.
                PRIORITY VARCHAR(5), -- The urgency level of the work order (e.g., '0', '1', '2').
                CREATED_TIME DATE, -- The timestamp when the work order was created. Use this for queries related to creation date or time.
                CREATED_BY VARCHAR(100), -- The person or system that created the work order.
                LAST_MODIFIED_TIME DATE, -- The last time the work order was changed.
                LAST_MODIFIED_BY VARCHAR(300), -- The person or system that last modified the work order.
                WORK_ORDER_KEY VARCHAR(300),
                INTERNAL_WORK_ORDER_ID VARCHAR(50),
                DISTRIBUTION_NAME VARCHAR(300), -- The name of the group or team the work order was assigned to.
                DISTRIBUTION_STATUS VARCHAR(300), -- The status of the work order's distribution.
                DISTRIBUTION_TYPE VARCHAR(300), -- The type of distribution for the work order.
                OPERATIONAL_GROUP_NAME VARCHAR(300), -- The name of the operational group responsible for the work order.
                ASSIGNEE_NAME VARCHAR(300), -- The name of the individual assigned to perform the work.
                ASSIGNEE_IS_ACTIVE VARCHAR(300), -- Indicates if the assigned person is currently active.
                JOB_TYPE VARCHAR(300), -- The type of job or task the work order represents.
                FACILITY VARCHAR(100), -- The physical building or location where the work is to be performed.
                REGION_NAME VARCHAR(100), -- The geographical region of the work order.
                WORK_ORDER_LANGUAGE VARCHAR(300), -- The language the work order is written in.
                DISTRIBUTION_OPERATIONAL_REGION_ID VARCHAR(300), -- The Region id of Distribution Operational for the Work Order.
                FACILITY_OPERATIONAL_REGION_ID VARCHAR(300), -- The Region id of Facility Operational for the Work Order.
                OPERATIONAL_GRP_OPERATIONAL_REGION_ID VARCHAR(300),
                ADDITIONAL_SERVICE_ID VARCHAR(300),
                ADDITIONAL_SERVICE_NAME VARCHAR(300), -- The name of any extra service related to the work order.
                ODS_UPDATE_DATE DATE, -- The date the record was last updated in the Operational Data Store.
                MD5_HASH VARCHAR(100),
                CONSTRAINT PK_WORK_ORDER PRIMARY KEY (WORK_ORDER_ID)
                );
